##A "hard core" epidemic prevention sample of a village party secretary in Hubei Province: The ninth day after the closure of the village, no confirmed cases | prism

Micro-signal Lengjing

Feature Introduction, tencent news product column, "Prism" focus on financial in-depth reports.

By Wang Xiao, editor | Yang Hao
Production | prism tencent Xiaoman studio

Welcome to download tencent news APP for more quality information

"I'm sitting at home now, I know who's playing Mahjong, who's bickering, who's coming back from Wuhan, " Yuan told prism by phone with confidence.

Yuan Shaomin is the secretary of Yuan Hu village, Dougang town, Xiaogan City, Hubei Province. Xiaogan is close to Wuhan, with convenient transportation and close contacts, while Yuanhu village is only 3-4 km from the city of Xiaogan. Therefore, the epidemic prevention and control of great difficulty and pressure.

As of February 1, a total of 749 confirmed cases of COVID-19 pneumonia had been reported in Xiaogan, with 5,428 close contacts being tracked and 5,066 under medical observation.

According to statistics, there are 1,600 villagers in Yuanhu village and 40 returnees from Wuhan. Not only that, many people in the village buy houses in the city of Xiaogan, frequently commuting between the village and the city.

"today is the ninth day of the closure of the village. There are no suspected or confirmed cases in our village. But we can not relax our vigilance, " yuan told prism on February 2.

It's not going to be easy at the moment.

Villages not only in Yuan Hu village, but also in Hubei and even in Henan are facing a similar situation: There are a large number of people returning home from Wuhan, the villagers do not have enough understanding of the dangers of the epidemic, and their human feelings are greater than the sky, make these villages become the focal point and difficulty of current epidemic prevention work.

"after several days of education, persuasion and other methods, the village has been quiet for two days, " Yuan said.

Yuan Shaomin would send his daily thoughts and feelings to his friends. Through the exchange with Yuan Shaomin and read his epidemic prevention "diary" , can be a glimpse of the real rural China.

"today is the eighth day of the closure of the village, and the results are slowly showing. We also hope that everyone will keep quiet and stick to it for seven days. Three village cadres, one injured and one sick (one sprained his foot while opening a green passage for a patient with fever the night before last) , really hope everyone will be quiet, yuan Shaomin wrote on his friends'circle.

Persuade 14 households to cancel "Xin Xiang"

Yuan Shaomin told prism, Xiaogan and Wuhan people flow, logistics close contacts. Village officials have been keeping a close eye on the new pneumonia since it emerged. After the confirmation of the new type of pneumonia, the village on the intensive publicity to wear masks, wash hands frequently.

Since January 23, villagers who have recently returned from or passed through Wuhan have been asked to register at the village clinic, check their temperature and be available for telephone interviews. At the same time, I suggest that you do not go out, if you have to go out to wear a mask.

Body temperature test for returnees in Yuanhu village

Xiaogan has a local "new fragrance" folk custom, that is, on the first day of the Lunar New Year, relatives and friends and family relatives together to mourn the death of the previous year, dense and complex personnel.

In addition, the village visits frequently during the Spring Festival in previous years. In accordance with local customs, the first day of the New Year, the village will be each other New Year; after the second day to Uncle New Year, the third day to in-law Parents New Year, the fourth day to Uncle New Year, there are many wedding, birthday party held intensively.

These activities carry a high risk of cross-infection in villages that value human face. In order to reduce the flow of personnel and personnel gathered, "new fragrance" and new year, marriage and other activities have to be cancelled.

"New Fragrance" is the most valued by the local people. And Yuan Shaomin's first stop was to work at his brother's house.

At that time, my brother had already bought the "new fragrance" ingredients, feel canceled on the face very sad to go.

"If we don't do it, we'll spend less money and suffer less. Who can bear the responsibility in case of infection? " Yuan advised. "If we can't pass it on face, the village secretary won't let us. "

After doing a good job as my brother, Yuan Shaomin and the village representative mobilized Benwan (there are seven bays in Yuan Hu village) and the other three families also cancelled the "new fragrance" . On the issue of "face" that everyone cares most, Yuan Shaomin stressed: "just say that the village secretary won't let you do it! "

Subsequently, we went to other bay mobilization, a total of 14 families canceled the "New Incense. ". Afterwards, the village propagandizes to everybody not to drop by the House, does not wish the New Year to be logical.

A total of 4 families in Yuanhu village cancelled their wedding activities, 3 cancelled their birthday celebrations, and other planned activities were abandoned or postponed.

It's not enough to stop the gathering in this village. Yuan Shaomin stressed that Yuanhu village is only 3-4 kilometers away from the city, to the surrounding towns only 2-3 kilometers, the flow of people is extremely complex, in order to prevent and control the spread of the epidemic must be "closed village. ".

"after realizing the seriousness of the epidemic, most of the villagers voluntarily requested the closure of the village, " Yuan said.

On the afternoon and evening of January 25, the villagers of Yuanhu village spontaneously sealed the eight intersections of the village with soil or tree branches, and the emergency passage was set up on the main road of the village.

Yuanhu village in the village to set up migrant population back point

The move predates the local requirement for unification. Xiaogan issued a notice on January 27, requiring villages to block access from January 28, but not to cut off transport networks, emergency transport routes and essential production materials.

A rant from a friend network

The closure of the village has also sparked controversy.

"At the beginning, some villagers didn't understand, and when they closed the village, some fled, some quarreled and some roughed up. Because some people didn't know enough about the epidemic, " Yuan said.

Cars are not allowed to enter the village, and some villagers have switched to using motorcycles and electric vehicles to go back and forth, increasing the gas pedal to rush through the mound, or carrying their cars across the barricade; some old people in the village are worried about the children in the city, who are going to deliver rice today and oil tomorrow, you want to see your wife or your grandkids.

The tree trunks used to block the road were sawed off at night, and the fuel pipes of the cars parked at the entrance to the village were pulled out. Others cycle back and forth along the treacherous, thorny, steep levees.

Yuanhu village with soil barrier village, forklift in the rear for emergency standby

Finally, the comprehensive comparison, or mound barrier is the most effective. However, Yuan Shaomin stressed that the construction forklift at the entrance of the emergency channel on standby to deal with emergency situations and transportation of necessities of life.

"I believe your evil, the city is so dangerous, a day so many new cases, all can not escape, why do you rush into the city, rush out of the city, rush back! " Yuan Shaomin in the circle of friends angry.

"In the past two days, the strongest reports from the public have been that there are one or two families or three or five people in the West Bay, always going in and out, and one or two in the East Bay, reflecting in particular the fact that there is an 'energy damselfly' who goes back and forth every day (as to which ones, I will not name here) . "people are saying that these people don't come in and out of here every day, and it's not my fault that I didn't warn them. "

After 25 years as the secretary of the village committee, Yuan Shaomin led the whole village from "poor nest" to become a model village of rural governance in the country. Mentioned in his circle of friends, it's as intimidating as a loudspeaker broadcast. In the village's seven wechat groups, he and village representatives have repeatedly stressed the need to go out as little as possible.

"I haven't cursed anyone in my long time as village secretary, or if I don't say something, it will be more serious. Everyone knows my temper. I also want to raise awareness, " Yuan said.

The villagers'council has a heavy responsibility

The tide began to turn on January 28th.

On January 27,73 new cases of pneumonia were confirmed in Xiaogan, up sharply from the previous period, Yuan told prism. Since then, villagers have become more aware of the epidemic around so serious, in order to maintain their own health and villagers, self-supervision of each other.

In recent days, anti-epidemic measures in many rural areas across the country have triggered heated discussions, with some villages closing roads with dirt, some village cadres guarding the entrance of villages to dissuade foreign visitors, and others refusing to open their doors when they pay new year calls.

Some netizens said the means "hard core" , but also accused these practices are not human, not civilized, compared to low.

"Some people don't understand the grassroots at all, " Yuan said gloomily. "The situation is different in every village, and everyone is trying to figure out their own working methods. "

He said that village cadres do not have the power to restrain the villagers, to do a good job of epidemic prevention and control, only by the villagers themselves recognize the seriousness of the epidemic, spontaneously formed joint prevention and control. "We should mobilize the masses to participate in the management of the countryside, mobilize all the people, and promote and supervise it on their own initiative. "

If the villagers do not have a high degree of self-awareness and self-discipline, then the village cadres visit the house every hour registration data will be different, and more dangerous.

A Village Party secretary in the Fuling District region of Chongqing also told prism that the epidemic prevention depended on voluntary supervision by villagers. The son of a local Party secretary returned home from Wuhan without a report and went out to preside over the work. The villagers eventually reported that more than 20 people who had close contact with him had been quarantined.

"No one from outside the village is allowed to come and go in the town, and everyone from this village has been told not to come back in advance. This was all at the villagers' own request. "

Yuan Shaomin told prism that the council was formed long ago by the villagers. In this epidemic prevention work, council members assume the responsibility of propagandist and supervisor.

"today is the eighth day of the closure of the village, the results are slowly showing, and I hope everyone will keep quiet. Persistence, persistence, persistence is victory, " yuan wrote on the evening of February 1 in his circle of friends.

With my consent, prism selected some of Yuan Shaomin's epidemic prevention "diary" :

22 January:
At present, the most effective way to prevent the epidemic situation is: propaganda, propaganda, propaganda again, don't want to listen to propaganda; drink water, drink water, drink more water, don't want to drink water, also drink water; mask, mask, mask, wear a mask if in trouble; wash hands, wash hands, wash hands more, wash hands before and after meals.
Yuan Shaomin wishes you a happy New Year, Pepsi Cola, non-toxic.

23 January:
Relatives in Yuanhu village: For the health of YOU and your family, as well as the health of your neighbors, relatives and friends, those relatives who come back from Wuhan or come back through Wuhan these days, please go to the village clinic to register with Dean Zhan Shaolin at any time to check your body temperature and accept telephone interview. ..
It is suggested that we should be cautious in paying New Year greetings this Spring Festival. If we can not go out, we should not go into cities or densely populated areas. If we have to go out, please wear a mask, wash hands and drink more water.

January 24,14:00 pm:
Give the villagers free masks, thanks to Wu Daichang, although everyone a guide is very important.

January 24,17:00 pm:
Don't worry about the two bottles of wine, two packets of sugar, a carton of cigarettes, or face-saving, filial piety time everywhere, at any time, not in these days. Health and life are worth more than face.
I solemnly declare, even if you insist on visiting, I will not receive, no one at home back to visit.
Do not visit each other is the best blessing, is the respect of health, is the greatest filial piety to the elderly.

26 January:
Rush a flash is a day, spot-check the temperature of key objects, visit key control of returnees, key publicity, separate household registration visit, will secretly into the village migrant persuade away..
It was a windy afternoon. It was cold. It was freezing. Don't catch a cold at this time.

27 January:
Once again, please do not go out, do not go back to the Yuan Lake village home, honestly stay in the bay each home, this is the respect for all of you, your behavior is the biggest contribution to the fight against this epidemic.

28 January:
I sincerely submit to you, you also believe the evil, the city is so dangerous, a day with so many new cases, can not escape, why do you rush into the city, rush out of the city rush back! Please take care of other people. ..
AGAIN, everybody! Everybody, please!
Don't leave the village, don't shuttle back and forth between the city and the village, stay at home, stay in the village, still endure ten days, things will improve, I believe our country will overcome this epidemic.

29 January:
It's been a long day like a soldier. I'm exhausted
If everyone could be disciplined and follow the rules, they would not be so tired.

30 January:
Mobilizing the masses to fight together, through the masses to do, the masses to see is the best publicity in the hearts of the people. The smaller the unit, the smaller the risk, outsiders into the bay (including village cadres) less, the less the means of transmission, let the masses do it! Don't overstep your bounds.

31 January:
Today we open the green channel, according to the pre-plan, send people to focus on the purchase of gas, bottled water, to ensure the supply of necessities.
The liquefied gas station was not open for business, the specialized store for barreling water in Henggang was out of stock, and some parts of the city were closed to traffic, leaving empty vehicles to return. These two items of daily necessities still need to be overcome for two or three more days.
No gas, cooking water to coal burning firewood, no wood stove with brick code, really no place to go to the Ridge of the field to dig a pot buried cooking, you often do (of course, this sentence is a joke) .
No bucket of water put frequently boil tap water to drink, drink boiled water is also safer. You might as well experience a traditional rural life.
No Rice, tomorrow to the office to buy, I have contacted the good run of the Eastern Wu Rice Long, their base has rice sales.
Try to get over it for two or three days, and the problem will soon be solved.

1 February:

Hang in there, hang in there, hang in there!

"today is the eighth day of the closure of the village, the results are slowly showing, and I hope everyone will keep quiet. Persistence, persistence, persistence is victory, " yuan wrote on the evening of February 1 in his circle of friends.

With my consent, prism selected some of Yuan Shaomin's epidemic prevention "diary" :

22 January:
At present, the most effective way to prevent the epidemic situation is: propaganda, propaganda, propaganda again, don't want to listen to propaganda; drink water, drink water, drink more water, don't want to drink water, also drink water; mask, mask, mask, wear a mask if in trouble; wash hands, wash hands, wash hands more, wash hands before and after meals.
Yuan Shaomin wishes you a happy New Year, Pepsi Cola, non-toxic.

23 January:
Relatives in Yuanhu village: For the health of YOU and your family, as well as the health of your neighbors, relatives and friends, those relatives who come back from Wuhan or come back through Wuhan these days, please go to the village clinic to register with Dean Zhan Shaolin at any time to check your body temperature and accept telephone interview. ..
It is suggested that we should be cautious in paying New Year greetings this Spring Festival. If we can not go out, we should not go into cities or densely populated areas. If we have to go out, please wear a mask, wash hands and drink more water.

January 24,14:00 pm:
Give the villagers free masks, thanks to Wu Daichang, although everyone a guide is very important.
Yuan Lake Village, 14 families to respond to the call of the government, in line with the trend, all cancelled the new incense activities, thank you for your cooperation and support.

January 24,17:00 pm:
Don't worry about the two bottles of wine, two packets of sugar, a carton of cigarettes, or face-saving, filial piety time everywhere, at any time, not in these days. Health and life are worth more than face.
I solemnly declare, even if you insist on visiting, I will not receive, no one at home back to visit.
Do not visit each other is the best blessing, is the respect of health, is the greatest filial piety to the elderly.

26 January:
Rush a flash is a day, spot-check the temperature of key objects, visit key control of returnees, key publicity, separate household registration visit, will secretly into the village migrant persuade away..
It was a windy afternoon. It was cold. It was freezing. Don't catch a cold at this time.

27 January:
Once again, please do not go out, do not go back to the Yuan Lake village home, honestly stay in the bay each home, this is the respect for all of you, your behavior is the biggest contribution to the fight against this epidemic.

28 January:
I sincerely submit to you, you also believe the evil, the city is so dangerous, a day with so many new cases, can not escape, why do you rush into the city, rush out of the city rush back! Please take care of other people. ..
AGAIN, everybody! Everybody, please!
Don't leave the village, don't shuttle back and forth between the city and the village, stay at home, stay in the village, still endure ten days, things will improve, I believe our country will overcome this epidemic.

29 January:
It's been a long day like a soldier. I'm exhausted
If everyone could be disciplined and follow the rules, they would not be so tired.

30 January:
Mobilizing the masses to fight together, through the masses to do, the masses to see is the best publicity in the hearts of the people. The smaller the unit, the smaller the risk, outsiders into the bay (including village cadres) less, the less the means of transmission, let the masses do it! Don't overstep your bounds.

31 January:
Today we open the green channel, according to the pre-plan, send people to focus on the purchase of gas, bottled water, to ensure the supply of necessities.
The liquefied gas station was not open for business, the specialized store for barreling water in Henggang was out of stock, and some parts of the city were closed to traffic, leaving empty vehicles to return. These two items of daily necessities still need to be overcome for two or three more days.
No gas, cooking water to coal burning firewood, no wood stove with brick code, really no place to go to the Ridge of the field to dig a pot buried cooking, you often do (of course, this sentence is a joke) .
No bucket of water put frequently boil tap water to drink, drink boiled water is also safer. You might as well experience a traditional rural life.
No Rice, tomorrow to the office to buy, I have contacted the good run of the Eastern Wu Rice Long, their base has rice sales.
Try to get over it for two or three days, and the problem will soon be solved.

1 February:
Today is the eighth day of the closure of the village, the results slowly show that we also hope to keep quiet, adhere to seven days.
Three village cadres, one injured and one sick (one sprained his ankle opening a green passage for a feverish patient the night before last) , really want everyone to be quiet.
Hang in there, hang in there, hang in there!

The tide began to turn on January 28th.

On January 27,73 new cases of pneumonia were confirmed in Xiaogan, up sharply from the previous period, Yuan told prism. Since then, villagers have become more aware of the epidemic around so serious, in order to maintain their own health and villagers, self-supervision of each other.

In recent days, anti-epidemic measures in many rural areas across the country have triggered heated discussions, with some villages closing roads with dirt, some village cadres guarding the entrance of villages to dissuade foreign visitors, and others refusing to open their doors when they pay new year calls.

Some netizens said the means "hard core" , but also accused these practices are not human, not civilized, compared to low.

"Some people don't understand the grassroots at all, " Yuan said gloomily. "The situation is different in every village, and everyone is trying to figure out their own working methods. "

He said that village cadres do not have the power to restrain the villagers, to do a good job of epidemic prevention and control, only by the villagers themselves recognize the seriousness of the epidemic, spontaneously formed joint prevention and control. "We should mobilize the masses to participate in the management of the countryside, mobilize all the people, and promote and supervise it on their own initiative. "

If the villagers do not have a high degree of self-awareness and self-discipline, then the village cadres visit the house every hour registration data will be different, and more dangerous.

A Village Party secretary in the Fuling District region of Chongqing also told prism that the epidemic prevention depended on voluntary supervision by villagers. The son of a local Party secretary returned home from Wuhan without a report and went out to preside over the work. The villagers eventually reported that more than 20 people who had close contact with him had been quarantined.

"No one from outside the village is allowed to come and go in the town, and everyone from this village has been told not to come back in advance. This was all at the villagers' own request. "
